<h3 class="h4 m3">Video playlists about Parenting</h3>
<div class='row row-skinny row-sm-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Advice to help you be a great parent</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/150/advice_to_help_you_be_a_great'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/parenting_playlist.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
11 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 34m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Kids don’t come with a manual, and parents don’t get grades to affirm they’re doing things right. These talks speak to the complexities of parenthood, offering unusual insights and hard-won advice.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Short talks for parents who are short on time but starved for intellectual stimulation</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/221/short_talks_for_parents_who_ar'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/parents_short_on_time.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>44:34</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>You aren't sleeping. You barely have time to eat, let alone peruse TED Talks. Here, talks under six minutes that will give you a quick dose of inspiration.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Talks to watch with the entire family</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/314/talks_to_watch_with_the_entire'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/whole_family.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 53m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>No matter the generation, these talks are perfect for bringing everyone together to learn, wonder and laugh.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

